; The project has a pre-existing peer-dep conflict between three@0.167.1
; and postprocessing@^6.37.6 (which wants three >= 0.168.0 < 0.185.0).
; Resolving that for real means bumping three to 0.184.x and re-validating
; every consumer (@react-three/*, gainmap-js, n8ao, drei). Until that
; cleanup happens, fall back to npm 6-style peer resolution so `npm install`
; works without flags on Vercel, in CI, and for local devs.
legacy-peer-deps=true
